title: Hurricane Eta survivors rescued by army helicopter in Guatemala
description: The Guatemalan army has dispatched helicopters to rescue survivors of Hurricane Eta. Footage shows families being lifted from rooftops in the town of San Cristobal Verapaz after severe flooding from the storm. The government believes at least 100 people have …
